Resource Profile: EPR policy set based on template 302

Official URL: http://fhir.ch/ig/ch-epr-fhir/StructureDefinition/PpqmConsentTemplate302 Version: 4.0.1-ballot-2
Active as of 2024-11-19 Computable Name: PpqmConsentTemplate302

Copyright/Legal: CC0-1.0

EPR policy set based on template 302 – gives a group of healthcare professionals read access to the patient's EPR, without delegation rights.

Usage:

  • Examples for this Resource Profile: Consent/PpqmConsentTemplate302Example
